---
title: Easy Mexican Pork Carnitas & Garlic Rice with Avocado Salsa & Sour Cream
description: This slow-cooker meal is a labour of love, but it’s well worth it; the juicy pork has been cooked down in a Mexican tomato-based sauce until fall-apart tender. No need to pick up a knife for this one - grab a fork and a spoon, and let this taste sensation embrace you.
